# Tauri
src-tauri/WixTools/

# NOTE: src-tauri/icons/ is INTENTIONALLY committed to the repo.
# The release workflow (.github/workflows/release.yml) runs on
# clean GitHub Actions runners and needs `icon.ico` (Windows),
# `icon.icns` (macOS), and the Linux PNG sizes to produce per-
# platform installers. Ignoring the whole directory breaks all
# three platform bundle steps with "icons/icon.ico not found".
# The ios/ and android/ sub-directories generated by
# `tauri icon` ARE ignored below — we don't ship mobile.
src-tauri/icons/android/
src-tauri/icons/ios/

# Logs
*.log

# Test coverage
coverage/
